Only on Nick.

00:18:03.610 --> 00:18:06.610
Watch me trick-free to those Cocoa Pibbles.

00:18:06.610 --> 00:18:07.610
Yes.

00:18:07.610 --> 00:18:10.610
Soco Cocoa, my favorite sumo wrestler.

00:18:10.610 --> 00:18:12.610
I must have something super chocolaty

00:18:12.610 --> 00:18:14.610
before entering the ring.

00:18:14.610 --> 00:18:17.610
Here, Mr. Soco, my Cocoa Pibbles.

00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:20.610
Ooh, humongous chocolaty taste.

00:18:20.610 --> 00:18:22.610
Come on, pal.

00:18:23.610 --> 00:18:24.610
Uh-oh.

00:18:24.610 --> 00:18:27.610
Ooh, Barney, you're not Soco.

00:18:27.610 --> 00:18:28.610
But I got you a cocoa.

00:18:28.610 --> 00:18:30.610
Post-Cocoa Pibble cereal.

