00:32:45.860 --> 00:32:47.860
What makes someone your best friend?

00:32:47.860 --> 00:32:49.860
I think it's that

00:32:49.860 --> 00:32:51.860
you laugh at the same thing.

00:32:51.860 --> 00:32:53.860
