00:32:53.860 --> 00:32:55.860
And sometimes, when you're together,

00:32:55.860 --> 00:32:57.860
you look at each other and you just know.

00:32:59.860 --> 00:33:01.860
Everything is perfect.

00:33:01.860 --> 00:33:03.860
Some people think you can't be best friends

00:33:03.860 --> 00:33:05.860
with your little brother.

00:33:05.860 --> 00:33:07.860
But with us it's easy.

00:33:07.860 --> 00:33:09.860
I guess we just have the same Pete way of looking at things.

00:33:14.710 --> 00:33:16.710
Ours was the kind of best friendship

00:33:16.710 --> 00:33:18.710
that seemed like it was built to last forever.

00:33:23.140 --> 00:33:27.580
How was I to know that a

00:33:27.580 --> 00:33:29.580
10 pound bowling ball

00:33:29.580 --> 00:33:31.580
was about to roll into our lives

00:33:31.580 --> 00:33:33.580
and destroy everything we stood for?

00:33:58.950 --> 00:34:41.210
Some say it was just a ball.

00:34:43.210 --> 00:34:45.210
But to my dad,

00:34:45.210 --> 00:34:47.210
it was a dual rotating pressure

00:34:47.210 --> 00:34:49.210
torqued hunk of engineering perfection.

00:34:51.210 --> 00:34:53.210
When it hit the slats,

00:34:53.210 --> 00:34:55.210
the sound of thunder shook the lanes.

00:34:55.210 --> 00:34:57.210
And so it got the name

00:34:57.210 --> 00:34:59.210
Rolling Thunder.

00:34:59.210 --> 00:35:01.210
I think my dad was more

00:35:01.210 --> 00:35:03.210
proud of his bowling ball than he was of me and Pete.

00:35:03.210 --> 00:35:05.210
But then one day,

00:35:05.210 --> 00:35:07.210
my dad's fingers got too big

00:35:07.210 --> 00:35:09.210
to fit inside its sacred holes.

00:35:09.210 --> 00:35:11.210
He worked out like crazy

00:35:11.210 --> 00:35:13.210
to try and get them back into shape.

00:35:13.210 --> 00:35:15.210
But it was no use.

00:35:15.210 --> 00:35:17.210
I guess he could have drilled the holes wider,

00:35:17.210 --> 00:35:19.210
but that would have ruined its delicate calibration.

00:35:19.210 --> 00:35:28.570
Finally,

00:35:28.570 --> 00:35:30.570
he realized what he had to do.

00:35:30.570 --> 00:35:32.570
The time had come to pass the ball down

00:35:32.570 --> 00:35:34.570
to the next generation.

00:35:34.570 --> 00:35:36.570
And that's how it all started.

00:35:36.570 --> 00:35:41.000
What if you could be rich forever?

00:35:41.000 --> 00:35:43.000
But you had to go to the bathroom

00:35:43.000 --> 00:35:45.000
