00:35:45.000 --> 00:35:48.820
Once a day?

00:35:48.820 --> 00:35:50.820
Yeah.

00:35:50.820 --> 00:35:54.170
I'd do it.

00:35:54.170 --> 00:35:56.170
What if you could get your driver's license now?

00:35:56.170 --> 00:35:58.170
But for six months,

00:35:58.170 --> 00:36:00.170
