00:36:00.170 --> 00:36:03.450
I already got one.

00:36:03.450 --> 00:36:05.450
How'd you do that?

00:36:05.450 --> 00:36:07.450
Pete, Pete, come here.

00:36:07.450 --> 00:36:09.450
We both wondered what dad

00:36:09.450 --> 00:36:11.450
was doing home on his bowling night.

00:36:11.450 --> 00:36:13.450
But then, we had an even bigger surprise.

00:36:13.450 --> 00:36:17.460
Some say

00:36:17.460 --> 00:36:19.460
he possessed the secrets of the universe.

00:36:19.460 --> 00:36:21.460
All we knew for sure was

00:36:21.460 --> 00:36:23.460
he used to fix dishwashers

00:36:23.460 --> 00:36:25.460
