00:36:25.460 --> 00:36:27.460
He was our dad's dad.

00:36:27.460 --> 00:36:31.740
Our grandfather.

00:36:31.740 --> 00:36:33.740
Oh, boys, I missed you.

00:36:33.740 --> 00:36:35.740
Because he lived so far away,

00:36:35.740 --> 00:36:37.740
