00:37:09.430 --> 00:37:11.430
But what you might not know is

00:37:11.430 --> 00:37:13.430
I also love another.

00:37:13.430 --> 00:37:15.430
Her name is

00:37:15.430 --> 00:37:17.430
Rolling Thunder.

00:37:17.430 --> 00:37:19.430
How touching.

00:37:19.430 --> 00:37:21.430
Some people say

00:37:21.430 --> 00:37:23.430
she's just a ball,

00:37:23.430 --> 00:37:25.430
but she's more. She's a friend,

00:37:25.430 --> 00:37:27.430
a teacher. She can pull you out

00:37:27.430 --> 00:37:29.430
of the eighth frame doldrums

00:37:29.430 --> 00:37:31.430
