Like a father, no?

00:39:39.860 --> 00:39:45.990
Engineering miracle.

00:39:45.990 --> 00:39:47.990
A power that can only be harnessed

00:39:47.990 --> 00:39:49.990
by a wiggly, you hear me?

00:39:49.990 --> 00:39:51.990
It must

00:39:51.990 --> 00:39:53.990
be passed on.

00:39:53.990 --> 00:39:55.990
And it must

00:39:55.990 --> 00:39:57.990
