01:35:39.660 --> 01:35:41.660
It's my mom's birthday.

01:35:41.660 --> 01:35:43.660
Sorry. Come back when you got the money.

01:35:43.660 --> 01:35:45.660
Does this mean we can go home now?

01:35:45.660 --> 01:35:47.660
Do you know what happens to bad kids?

01:35:47.660 --> 01:35:49.660
I mean really bad kids like you.

01:35:49.660 --> 01:35:51.660
No, why don't you tell me?

01:35:51.660 --> 01:35:53.660
I don't know.

01:35:53.660 --> 01:35:55.660
No, why don't you tell me?

01:35:55.660 --> 01:35:58.660
Whenever you get snotty with somebody,

01:35:58.660 --> 01:36:01.660
whenever you hurt someone,

01:36:01.660 --> 01:36:03.660
whenever you're selfish or insult somebody...

01:36:03.660 --> 01:36:06.660
Yeah, yeah, I better not pout, I better not shout,

01:36:06.660 --> 01:36:08.660
because Santa Claus is coming to town.

01:36:08.660 --> 01:36:11.660
Sam, whenever you're bad, and that means when you steal,

01:36:11.660 --> 01:36:17.760
Crimson Clown is watching you.

01:36:17.760 --> 01:36:21.360
Ooh.

01:36:21.360 --> 01:36:23.360
Watch out, Sam, or it'll get you.

01:36:23.360 --> 01:36:25.360
Ooh, I'm scared.

01:36:25.360 --> 01:36:27.360
Don't believe me. You'll see.

01:36:27.360 --> 01:36:45.970
Now we're late, and I'm just gonna be tipped.

01:36:45.970 --> 01:36:47.970
Well, who cares?

01:36:47.970 --> 01:36:50.970
You should, because of you. We don't have a gift for her.

01:36:50.970 --> 01:36:52.970
Just put some cash in a car. She'll be happy.

01:36:52.970 --> 01:36:54.970
You stole my cash, remember?

01:36:54.970 --> 01:36:56.970
Why don't you ask your pal to Crimson Clown?

01:36:56.970 --> 01:37:04.470
Come on, let's go.

01:37:04.470 --> 01:37:19.620
Tell mom we'll be right down.

01:37:19.620 --> 01:37:20.620
Yeah, whatever.

01:37:20.620 --> 01:37:25.090
Where have you been?

01:37:25.090 --> 01:37:27.090
Look at the time!

01:37:27.090 --> 01:37:29.090
Where's Michael?

01:37:29.090 --> 01:37:31.090
Um, upstairs.

01:37:31.090 --> 01:37:33.090
I told you to be back at six.

01:37:33.090 --> 01:37:39.800
I'm sorry, Mom.

01:37:39.800 --> 01:37:41.800
I wanted to come home,

01:37:41.800 --> 01:37:43.800
but Mike said he wanted to see his friends,

01:37:43.800 --> 01:37:45.800
and he didn't care how late we'd be.

01:37:45.800 --> 01:37:49.340
Oh, is that right?

01:37:49.340 --> 01:37:50.340
Well, we'll just see about that.

01:37:50.340 --> 01:37:52.340
Michael, get down here right now.

01:37:52.340 --> 01:37:57.450
You know what? Why are you so late?

01:37:57.450 --> 01:37:59.450
And what's this I hear about you're not caring

01:37:59.450 --> 01:38:00.450
what time you get home,

01:38:00.450 --> 01:38:03.450
especially when you have your little brother to look after?

01:38:03.450 --> 01:38:06.450
I mean, how many times do I have to tell you this?

01:38:06.450 --> 01:38:09.450
You have to do your homework, you have to have a bath,

01:38:09.450 --> 01:38:11.450
we haven't even had dinner.

01:38:11.450 --> 01:38:15.450
I've been telling you this kind of thing since you were five years old!

01:38:15.450 --> 01:38:18.450
Now, listen, I have to be able to count on you.

01:38:18.450 --> 01:38:20.450
You're the man of the house.

01:38:20.450 --> 01:38:22.450
Look at me, young man, when I talk to you.

01:38:22.450 --> 01:38:24.450
Now, I want you to get up in your room,

01:38:24.450 --> 01:38:26.450
and I don't want to hear one word out of you

01:38:26.450 --> 01:39:04.290
until dinner's on the table. Is that clear?

01:39:04.290 --> 01:39:07.460
Yeah?

01:39:07.460 --> 01:39:09.460
supper will be ready soon. Wash up.

01:39:09.460 --> 01:39:10.460
Okay.

01:39:10.460 --> 01:39:16.720
Are you okay?

01:39:16.720 --> 01:39:18.720
Sure, Mom.

01:39:18.720 --> 01:39:20.720
Just mad at Mike for getting you so upset.

01:39:20.720 --> 01:39:22.720
Don't worry about it. Let's go.

01:39:22.720 --> 01:39:42.540
Very funny. Dinner's ready.

01:39:42.540 --> 01:39:45.540
Don't make Mom any mader than she already is.

01:39:45.540 --> 01:40:08.960
Afraid of the dark? Stay in the glow of the couch,

01:40:08.960 --> 01:40:10.960
