There you went, Phil.

01:40:51.960 --> 01:40:53.960
Hey, Kirby.

01:40:53.960 --> 01:40:55.960
Didn't I pass you on the way in?

01:40:55.960 --> 01:40:58.960
When it comes to great taste in Eggo Waffles,

