Now, the sneaking begins again,

01:41:28.920 --> 01:41:44.660
with Are You Afraid of the Dark?

01:41:44.660 --> 01:41:45.660
Mike.

01:41:45.660 --> 01:41:48.660
All right.

01:41:48.660 --> 01:41:50.660
Can I watch TV?

01:41:50.660 --> 01:41:51.660
Sure, honey.

01:41:51.660 --> 01:42:56.790
And it came out.

01:42:56.790 --> 01:43:03.090
What are you staring at, turd face?

01:43:03.090 --> 01:43:06.090
All right, Sam, it's time for bed.

01:43:06.090 --> 01:43:09.090
Can I stay up a little bit longer?

01:43:09.090 --> 01:43:10.090
Yeah, Mom.

01:43:10.090 --> 01:43:13.090
He could watch a really scary horror movie.

01:43:13.090 --> 01:43:15.090
Sam would love that.

01:43:15.090 --> 01:43:17.090
That's okay.

01:43:17.090 --> 01:43:19.090
Wimp.

01:43:19.090 --> 01:43:21.090
I'm not, you overgrown dirtbag.

01:43:21.090 --> 01:43:24.090
Whoa, keep it up, and that crimson clown will get you.

01:43:24.090 --> 01:43:26.090
Cut it out with this stupid clown stuff.

01:43:26.090 --> 01:43:29.090
I know what you're doing, and I'm not scared.

01:43:29.090 --> 01:43:34.130
What's wrong with him?

01:43:34.130 --> 01:43:35.130
I don't know.

01:43:35.130 --> 01:43:37.130
We're at the stoo...

01:43:37.130 --> 01:43:38.130
Ice rink.

01:43:38.130 --> 01:43:40.130
And he was being a pain,

01:43:40.130 --> 01:43:42.130
