01:43:42.130 --> 01:43:44.130
a crimson clown will get him.

01:43:44.130 --> 01:43:45.130
Mike.

01:43:45.130 --> 01:43:47.130
I didn't even think he was listening.

01:43:47.130 --> 01:43:48.130
He never listens to anybody.

01:43:48.130 --> 01:43:50.130
I just gave him a break, sweetie.

01:43:50.130 --> 01:43:51.130
He's still little.

01:43:51.130 --> 01:43:53.130
Yeah, a little jerk.

01:43:53.130 --> 01:43:57.210
You're the jerk, Mike.

01:43:57.210 --> 01:44:09.100
You geek.

01:44:09.100 --> 01:44:10.100
Now what?

01:44:10.100 --> 01:44:55.480
Nothing!

01:44:55.480 --> 01:46:53.450
I had to sleep, or Mom will kill you.

01:46:53.450 --> 01:46:58.390
What do you care?

01:46:58.390 --> 01:47:00.390
Hey, Sam.

01:47:00.390 --> 01:47:03.390
That's the stuff I said about the clown.

01:47:03.390 --> 01:47:04.390
It isn't true, you know.

01:47:04.390 --> 01:47:06.390
I was just mad at you.

01:47:06.390 --> 01:47:08.390
Yeah, whatever.

01:47:08.390 --> 01:48:21.300
It was a dream.

01:48:21.300 --> 01:51:11.000
I opened it out?

01:51:11.000 --> 01:51:26.940
From me.

01:51:26.940 --> 01:51:27.940
And Sam.

01:51:27.940 --> 01:51:30.380
Beautiful.

01:51:30.380 --> 01:51:34.020
Thank you both.

01:51:34.020 --> 01:51:36.740
Sam got what he asked for.

01:51:36.740 --> 01:51:37.740
Happy birthday, Mom.

01:51:37.740 --> 01:51:38.740
Another chance.

01:51:38.740 --> 01:51:39.740
Happy birthday, Mom.

01:51:39.740 --> 01:51:42.740
Every kid deserves another chance.

01:51:42.740 --> 01:51:46.740
And the crimson clown gave him his.

01:51:46.740 --> 01:51:48.740
With a little help from Mike.

01:51:48.740 --> 01:51:50.740
That is a great story.

01:51:50.740 --> 01:51:51.740
Yeah.

01:51:51.740 --> 01:51:53.740
What did you think, Tucker?

01:51:53.740 --> 01:52:12.230
I'll do my own socks.

01:52:12.230 --> 01:52:13.230
Yes.

01:52:13.230 --> 01:52:24.960
What are you doing?

01:52:24.960 --> 01:52:25.960
You might need it.

01:52:25.960 --> 01:52:27.960
I doubt it.

01:52:27.960 --> 01:52:30.960
So, uh, we going out or what?

01:52:30.960 --> 01:52:35.960
Well, like Gary said, what goes around comes around.

01:52:35.960 --> 01:52:37.960
It's a real hot offer.

01:52:37.960 --> 01:52:42.960
But I just think you need to cool off.

01:52:42.960 --> 01:52:49.380
Can I walk you home?

01:52:49.380 --> 01:52:51.380
Sure.

